  <section>
    <h2>Usage Notes</h2>
    <layout-text>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Accessibility:</strong> Use <code>visually-hidden</code> text for icon-only triggers</li>
        <li><strong>Separators:</strong> Use <code>&lt;li role="separator"&gt;</code> to group related items</li>
        <li><strong>Danger actions:</strong> Add <code>class="danger"</code> for destructive actions</li>
        <li><strong>Keyboard:</strong> Arrow keys navigate, Enter/Space select, Escape closes</li>
        <li><strong>Placement:</strong> The dropdown auto-adjusts if there isn't enough space</li>
      </ul>
    </layout-text>
  </section>

